Sentencas: Novel core-shell SDC (Ce0.8SM0.2O1.9)/amorphous Na2CO3 nanocomposite was prepared for the first time.
Titulo: Novel core-shell SDC/amorphous Na2CO3 nanocomposite electrolyte for low-temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The core-shell nanocomposite particles are smaller than 100 nm with amorphous Na2CO3 shell of 46 nm in thickness.
Titulo: Novel core-shell SDC/amorphous Na2CO3 nanocomposite electrolyte for low-temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: The nanocomposite electrolyte shows superionic conductivity above 300 degrees C, where the conductivity reaches over 0.1 S cm(-1).
Titulo: Novel core-shell SDC/amorphous Na2CO3 nanocomposite electrolyte for low-temperature SOFCs

Sentencas: Such high conductive nanocomposite has been applied in low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (LTSOFCs) with an excellent performance of 0.8 W cm(-2) at 550 degrees C. A new potential approach of designing and developing superionic conductors for LTSOFCs was presented to develop interface as 'superionic highway' in two-phase materials based on coated SDC.
Titulo: Novel core-shell SDC/amorphous Na2CO3 nanocomposite electrolyte for low-temperature SOFCs
